<div class="invite">
  Hey! After the video, stick around because I want to chat...
</div>
<div class="box">
  <div id="player"></div>
</div>
<div id="chat">
  <h1 class="special">#FallingPlates</h1>
  <div id="willyoufollow">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <small class="text-muted">Jesus Asks</small>
        <br>
        Will you follow me?
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="btn btn-danger btn-block disabled">No</div>
        <div class="btn btn-danger btn-block disabled">I follow another religion</div>
        <div class="btn btn-warning btn-block disabled">I am not sure</div>
        <div class="btn btn-info btn-block" id="start-btn" onClick="$('#willyoufollow').hide();$('#myfriends').fadeIn();">I want to start</div>
        <div class="btn btn-success btn-block disabled">I am trying</div>
        <div class="btn btn-success btn-block disabled">I am following you</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="myfriends">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <p class="lead name_box">
          Hey &nbsp;<span class="name"></span>.
        </p>
        <p>That"s great you want to start to follow Jesus. Sometimes, it"s easier to start something new when a friend is involved.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div id="friends">
          <p id="connect_link" style="display:none">
            <%= link_to("Connect to Facebook and we'll find one of your friends for you to chat with", "#", onclick: "FB.login($.godchat.getFacebookId())") %>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="other_connections">
          <h3>
            Otherwise:
          </h3>
          <div class="btn btn-primary btn-block" id="invite-btn" onClick="$("#myfriends").hide();$("#linkafriend").fadeIn();">Invite a Christian friend</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="linkafriend">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <p class="lead">You can invite your friend by sharing the link below with them via Facebook.</p>
        <input class="form-control" id="link" onClick="this.select();" readonly="readonly" value="http://godchat.tv/u/06dEQ">
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p class="new-article">While you wait why not look through the article “Starting with God”, I have just loaded it into the media box to the left.</p>
        <p class="old-article">While we wait for your friend, you can keep reading the "Starting with God" article.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-default btn-sm btn-block" id="findsomeone-btn" onClick="$("#linkafriend").hide();$("#opconnect").fadeIn();">Find someone for me instead</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="opconnect">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <p class="lead">
          I"m busy searching for someone to chat with you.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p class="new-article">While you wait why not look through the article “Starting with God”, I have just loaded it into the media box to the left.</p>
        <p class="old-article">While I look for someone to chat with, you can keep reading the "Starting with God" article.</p>
        <div class="text-right">
          <i class="icon-spinner icon-spin"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="chatbox">
    <h1 class="special">#FallingPlates Chat</h1>
    <ul class="conversation">
      <li>
        <div class="message text-right">Hey, how are you?</div>
        <div class="timestamp pull-right">Just now</div>
        <div class="person">Robert</div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="message">Great. How do I get started?</div>
        <div class="timestamp pull-right">Just now</div>
        <div class="person">You</div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <input class="form-control chat-input" placeholder="Message..." type="text">
  </div>
</div>
<div id="fb-root"></div></div>